</style><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">代代木动画学院评论</h3><p>近年来，VTuber产业迅速普及，不仅在日本，在海外也已发展成为拥有热情粉丝的庞大娱乐产业。对于那些想要在行业中接受这样的挑战的人来说，我们学校提供了一个环境和机会，让他们可以从基础知识中学习，并获得迈出第一步的信心。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="H29zY8yt4A"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-operator-anycolor-vtuber-training-project-virtual-talent-academy-vta-resumes/">Nijisanji运营的ANYCOLOR VTuber培训项目“Virtual Talent Academy（VTA）”已恢复</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“由 Nijisanji 运营的 ANYCOLOR 的 VTuber 培训项目“虚拟人才学院（VTA）”已恢复” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-operator-anycolor-vtuber-training-project-virtual-talent-academy-vta-resumes/embed/#?secret=FismwX9dwf#?secret=H29zY8yt4A" data-secret="H29zY8yt4A" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="xX4CNFAsvX"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-training-project-virtual-talent-academy-by-anycolor-of-nijisanji-19-out-of-29-students-disappeared/">Nijisanji运营的ANYCOLOR VTuber培训项目29名成员中有19人失踪</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Nijisanji 运营的 ANYCOLOR VTuber 培训项目的 29 名成员中，有 19 人失踪” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-training-project-virtual-talent-academy-by-anycolor-of-nijisanji-19-out-of-29-students-disappeared/embed/#?secret=txW4pZTcEJ#?secret=xX4CNFAsvX" data-secret="xX4CNFAsvX" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000162.000027285.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="代代木动画学院开设新的“VTuber课程”！">代代木动画学院开设新的“VTuber课程”！</a></p><cite>公关时报</cite></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://www.yoani.co.jp/lp/vtuber/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="VTuber部门">VTuber部门</a></p><cite>代代木动画学院</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp 经营代表“Mr.2（暂定）”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber 信息）</p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/yoyogi-animation-academy-opened-vtuber-course-curriculum-supervised-by-anycolor-of-nijisanji/">后代代木动画学院「VTuber课程」开始，虹山寺ANYCOLOR合作监修课程</a>首发于<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> 。; https://p2y.jp/yoyogi-animation-academy-opened-vtuber-course-curriculum-supervised-by-anycolor-of-nijisanji/feed/ 0 108391
